  "task_html": "<div class=\"task-block task-blue\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Situation</div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin:0;\">Ein Taxi kostet <strong>3 &euro; Grundgeb&#xFC;hr</strong> plus <strong>1,50 &euro; pro Kilometer</strong>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"task-block task-orange\" style=\"margin-top:12px;\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Aufgabe a) &ndash; Wertetabelle erg&#xE4;nzen</div>\n  <div class=\"tbl-wrap\">\n    <table>\n      <thead><tr><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">Kilometer (x)</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">0</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">2</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">5</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">10</th></tr></thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td class=\"row-label\">Kosten f(x) in &euro;</td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"3\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"6\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"10.5\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"18\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"task-block task-green\" style=\"margin-top:12px;\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Aufgabe b) &ndash; Steigung und y-Achsenabschnitt</div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:0 0 10px 0;\">Trage m und b ein.</p>\n  <div class=\"tbl-wrap\">\n    <table>\n      <thead><tr><th style=\"background:#16a34a;\">Steigung m</th><th style=\"background:#16a34a;\">y-Achsenabschnitt b</th></tr></thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"1.5\" placeholder=\"m\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"3\" placeholder=\"b\"></td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n  <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkStation(8)\">&#x2713; &#xDC;berpr&#xFC;fen</button>\n  <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetStation(8)\">&#x21BA; Zur&#xFC;cksetzen</button>\n  <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-8\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"task-block task-orange\" style=\"margin-top:14px;\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Aufgabe c) &ndash; Aufgabe abgeben</div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:0;\">Wie viel kostet eine Fahrt von 15 km? Rechne auf Papier und gib die Aufgabe ab.</p>\n</div>",
  "sol_html": "<div style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\">\n  <strong>a) Wertetabelle:</strong><br>\n  <span style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;\">f(0)=3 &euro; | f(2)=6 &euro; | f(5)=10,50 &euro; | f(10)=18 &euro;</span><br><br>\n  <strong>b) Funktionsgleichung:</strong><br>\n  m = <strong>1,5</strong> (pro km), b = <strong>3</strong> (Grundgeb&#xFC;hr)<br>\n  <span style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;\">f(x) = 1,5x + 3</span><br><br>\n  <strong>c) 15 km:</strong><br>\n  <span style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;\">f(15) = 1,5 &middot; 15 + 3 = 22,5 + 3 = <strong>25,50 &euro;</strong></span>\n</div>"
}